932
01:05:05,898 --> 01:05:08,358
Let's go this way.

933
01:05:09,148 --> 01:05:13,608
The air is nice outside, too.

934
01:05:13,608 --> 01:05:18,008
Today is... perfect for the angry scene...

935
01:05:23,778 --> 01:05:25,548
Assistant Director.

936
01:05:26,288 --> 01:05:27,568
Just one second.

937
